modules.description: Emits and handles events with custom handlers, supporting metrics collection and instrumentation. Works with event records, handlers, and event registries. Used to track request durations, count errors, and monitor system health in real-time.

Tracks and processes custom events like `Web_request_done`, allowing handlers to respond to specific metrics. Works with a polymorphic variant type `event` to represent different kinds of telemetry data. Used to log latency information or trigger alerts based on emitted events.
